*Letchworth (1953)
*RAFFC (1937)
*Rushden Town (1954)
*Queens Park Rangers &#x27;A&#x27; (1948)
*Sheringham (1937)
*Stevenage Athletic (1974)
*Tunbridge Wells (1954)

Approached by the league but declined
*Brentford &#x27;A&#x27; (1947, 1948)
*Charlton Athletic &#x27;A&#x27;, (1948)
*Fulham &#x27;A&#x27; (1948)
